Annual net precipitation (precipitation minus evaporation) entering the Arctic Ocean domain (shown in the included figure), in km3/yr. Arctic Ocean domain is bounded by Nares Strait, Barrow Strait, The Barents Sea Opening and Fram Strait. Includes precipitation and evaporation from sea ice and the ocean.

Annual net precipitation (precipitation minus evaporation) entering the Arctic Ocean domain (shown in the included figure), in km3/yr. Arctic Ocean domain is bounded by Nares Strait, Barrow Strait, The Barents Sea Opening and Fram Strait. Includes precipitation and evaporation from sea ice and the ocean. Convention for the fluxes is that positive fluxes signify a source of FW to the Arctic and negative fluxes are a sink/export of FW for the Arctic.
